#: core/analyzers/explain_analysis.py:1600
msgid ""
"Options (listed by typical effectiveness): (1) Drop CLUSTER BY before the "
"one-shot load, run OPTIMIZE FULL afterwards to re-cluster; (2) Disable eager"
" clustering via `ALTER TABLE ... SET TBLPROPERTIES "
"('delta.liquid.forceDisableEagerClustering' = 'True')` and run OPTIMIZE FULL"
" afterwards — keeps LC metadata and skips write-time re-shuffle; (3) Reduce "
"the number of clustering keys if read-side pruning still holds; (4) Disable "
"Hierarchical Clustering if enabled and not strictly needed; (5) Scale up the"
" warehouse temporarily for this INSERT; (6) Split the load into smaller "
"batches so each shuffle fits in memory."
msgstr ""
"選択肢（一般的な効果順）: (1) 一回限りのロード前に CLUSTER BY を外し、後に OPTIMIZE FULL で再クラスタリング; (2) "
"eager clustering を `ALTER TABLE ... SET TBLPROPERTIES "
"('delta.liquid.forceDisableEagerClustering' = 'True')` で無効化し、後で OPTIMIZE "
"FULL — LC メタデータ保持・書き込み時 re-shuffle スキップ; (3) 読み取りプルーニングが効くならクラスタリングキー数を削減; "
"(4) Hierarchical Clustering が必須でなければ無効化; (5) この INSERT 中だけウェアハウスをスケールアップ; "
"(6) ロードを小バッチに分割し各 shuffle がメモリに収まるよう調整。"

#: core/analyzers/hash_analysis.py:90
